      "raw_text": "1t has been definitely decided by\nthe Washington Water Power COM\npany to extend their Astor street\nline to connect with the Lidgerwood\nline. and the city council will be ask\ned at once to grant a franchise 70\nthe company for the extension.\n\n\nThe company has franchise along\nsome OF the streets. but will ask for\nan entirely new one\n\n\nThe new line Will give the Lidger-\nwood park people the same service\nas the Pacific avenue line, every ten\nminutes."
